---------------------------------------------------------------------------

                                  INSTALL

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

  1) It is assumed you have already installed the following:

       Tools:

         * ocamlfind
         * omake

       OCaml-bindings:

         * lacaml
         * gsl

     You may want to use Godi to facilitate the installation.

  2) Enter "omake install" to install the library using ocamlfind.

  3) Enter "omake" in the doc-directory to build the PDF-manual "gpr.pdf".

Enjoy!

